<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sort-vt">sort <strong><em>vt</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /sɔːt/    美 /sɔːrt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>把...分类 / 整理：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>sorted</strong> the apples <strong>into</strong> big ones and small ones.
他把这些苹果分成大小两类。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="sort-out-from">sort out (from)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>(从…中) 挑选出；整理；处理：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We should sort out enemies from friends.
我们应该分清敌友。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Jane admits that she can’t sort out all the mess in the households.
简承认她根本处理不好家庭的麻烦事。</p><footer>2013 湖北改</footer></div></div>